## Language to Avoid (strict)

### Hype / performance

- crushed, insane, game-changing, revolutionary

### Authority cosplay

- obviously, clearly, as we all know

### Vague evaluation

- important, interesting, powerful (without explanation)

### AI-coded verbs

- delve, embrace, empower, foster, navigate, unveil, enhance

### AI-coded nouns

- landscape, realm, tapestry, journey (unless literal)

### Boilerplate transitions

- furthermore, moreover, additionally, in conclusion

### Structural tells

- repetitive sentence length
- excessive hedging
- over-clean, over-numbered layouts

